== Summary ==
Alt text: A real-life photo of a black city lightpost, with a banner that showcases furry VRChat avatars (two Rexouiums, a Novabeast, and a deer with fangs) on a graphic for Furry Weekend Atlanta. The banner reads "Atlanta welcomes FWA - Furry Weekend Atlanta, May 8-11, 2025 - Atlanta Marriott Marquis". Behind the lightpost, are distant hotels, the Marriott Marquis, and the Hilton.

Date of photo: May 12, 2025

Location of photo: John Portman Boulevard NE, Atlanta, Georgia, USA

Photographer: [[User:DAG-XR]]
